resource.http://dev.llgc.org.uk/sas/full_text:
Romulus and Remus
Romulus is the legendary founder of the city of Rome after killing his brother, Remus.
The creation of the city of Rome is traditionally dated in 753.
resource.chars:
Romulus and Remus

Romulus is the legendary founder of the city of Rome after killing his brother, Remus.

The creation of the city of Rome is traditionally dated in 753.

resource.http://dev.llgc.org.uk/sas/full_text: According to legend, Romulus and Remus were rescued by a she-wolf that fed them. She quickly became one of the emblems of Rome and also appears on the coins.
